<h2 id="1-check-cookies">1. Check cookies</h2>

<ul>
  <li>From HTTP Response Headers:
    <div class="language-http highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="err">...
Set-Cookie: access_token=divination:student
...
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

