<h2 id="2-change-the-value-of-access_token">2. Change the value of <strong>access_token</strong></h2>

<ul>
  <li>HTTP Request Headers:
    <div class="language-http highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="err">...
Cookie: access_token=divination:professor
...
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Changing the value to <strong>divination:professor</strong> returns:
    <div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>OMG! You're so fortunate! Take this flag: TG19{what_a_fortune_my_lucky_one}
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

